      section.voice-and-tone#why-is-word
        h4.purple-border Why is word choice important
        p Words can establish credibility, motivate action, and most importantly, differentiate data.world in good ways. 
        p If we sound like everyone else, or if we don’t clearly describe what we do and why we do it, we will never be more than a blip on the radar. 
        p We’re not a “blip” company. 
        br
        h4.purple-border Shibboleths
        p.italic A use of language regarded as distinctive of a particular group
        p Marketing-speak, VC buzzwords, and other jargon will alienate our broader community in pursuit of the small sliver of that community that responds well.
        p Our community draws from data workers, civic volunteers, data journalists, and other technical and idealistic groups. They are justifiably “marketing averse.” They will run from language that marks us as outsiders or in it for the “wrong” reasons.
        br
        
        
        
